          "text": "<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-598d18df-7fff-760c-7025-86c182dee0f6\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">A Eugenia azeda, popularmente conhecida como ubaia-azeda, ou também como pitanga-feijoa, uvaia da praia ou uvaia das dunas, é uma espécie da família Myrtaceae e é nativa e endêmica do Brasil, ocorrendo na região Nordeste, nos estados do Ceará e Rio Grande do Norte, especificamente em áreas de restinga.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Trata-se de um arbusto que atinge entre 1 e 3 metros de altura. Apresenta flores pequenas e brancas, e sua frutificação ocorre entre os meses de novembro e dezembro. Os frutos são pequenos, arredondados e de cor amarelo-alaranjada, podendo ser consumidos in natura, apesar do sabor azedo ou ácido, que lembra uma mistura de uvaia com abacaxi. Além disso, os frutos são versáteis e podem ser utilizados no preparo de sucos, doces, recheios para bolos e sorvetes.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Devido à sua beleza e porte, a ubaia-azeda também possui potencial ornamental e pode ser cultivada com facilidade em pequenos jardins.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Referências:</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:12pt;margin-bottom:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Eugenia</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">in</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Flora e Funga do Brasil.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> Jardim Botânico do Rio de Janeiro. Disponível em: https://floradobrasil.jbrj.gov.br/FB126980. Acesso em: 14 jul. 2025</span></p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> UBAIA-AZEDA (</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Eugenia azeda</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">). </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Projeto colecionando frutas.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> Disponível em: https://www.colecionandofrutas.com.br/eugeniaazeda.htm. Acesso em: 25 jun. 2025.</span>",
